Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Bah, there's nothing to buy here. I'm heading
home.

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Hmm, why'd I come here again? I needed to
buy...something.

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Phew. Funny thing, as you get older, everything
starts gettin' heavier.

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
I, um, I can't quite remember where my house
is.

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Where did you come from? ...Oh, you live here,
eh?

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Hmm? Why am I here? I think I was heading out
for a walk, and then, um...

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Hmm? What did I come here for...?

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
Hmm? Why is there a big town around my
house?

<NAME_MOB_DONALD>
I could swear this town was a whole lot smaller.
Am I in the wrong place?
